{"title":"一枚邮票","authors":["彭国梁"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":10,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"·一枚邮票·"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彭国梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一枚比月光还薄的邮票"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抖动着翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻飞在城市与乡村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人群和人群之间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寻找心灵的伴侣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有的邮票出发时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都驮着美好的愿望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都摇晃着身子朝幸福和愉快飞去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一枚邮票带来的消息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可以使年轻的突然苍老"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可以让阴雨天即刻转晴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而更多的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寻觅爱情的找到仇恨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"找寻阳光的带回寒风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深深的痛苦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深深的幸福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都被人们久久珍藏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间的手掌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抹去了平凡的事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论匆匆的岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带来多少值得心爱的东西"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渴望情感的人们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依旧钟爱着一枚小小的邮票"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依旧相信——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一枚邮票会产生奇迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能改变自己的一生"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}